1. *Stižu* gosti sutra uveče. (Guests are arriving tomorrow evening.)
2. Svakog dana *stizala* je nova pošta. (Every day new mail arrived.)
3. Rekli su da će pomoć *stići* uskoro. (They said that help will arrive soon.)
4. Da li znate kada *stizu* novi studenti? (Do you know when the new students are arriving?)
5. Moramo da požurimo, voz *stize* za pet minuta. (We have to hurry, the train is arriving in five minutes.)
6. Kada *stignu* informacije, obavestiću vas odmah. (As soon as the information arrives, I will let you know.)
7. *Stižući* na cilj, trkač je pao i povredio se. (While arriving at the finish line, the runner fell and got injured.)
8. Da li si video ko *stize*? (Have you seen who is arriving?)
9. Nemoj da kasniš, svi su već *stigli*. (Don't be late, everyone has already arrived.)
10. *Stizali* su upozorenja o lošem vremenu, ali niko nije očekivao ovakvu oluju. (Warnings about bad weather were arriving, but no one expected such a storm.)